Package: soovee-common
Architecture: all
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: python-soovee, python-eyed3, python-xdg, ${python:Depends}, 
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: SooVee Serial Audio Manager - Common
 A serial audio manager for serial audio feed subscription services like 
 Podiobooks. Contains the common soovee components for soovee-cli and 
 soovee-gui packages.

