Package: soovee
Architecture: all
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: soovee-gui, soovee-cli, ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SooVee Serial Audio Manager
 A serial audio manager for serial audio feed subscription services like 
 Podiobooks. Meta package to install soovee-cli and soovee-gui packages.
